flowchart TD
    Pending[EvidenceFile pending] --> Kind{Detected file kind}
    Kind -- PDF --> PdfOptimize[Ghostscript optimize]
    PdfOptimize --> PdfThumb[PyMuPDF first page thumbnail]
    Kind -- Image --> ImageOptimize[Pillow WebP optimize]
    ImageOptimize --> ImageThumb[Tiny WebP thumbnail]
    Kind -- Archive --> ArchiveRewrite[Safe archive rewrite when possible]
    Kind -- Other --> KeepOriginal[Keep original file]
    PdfThumb --> UpdateRecord[Update storage paths and sizes]
    ImageThumb --> UpdateRecord
    ArchiveRewrite --> UpdateRecord
    KeepOriginal --> UpdateRecord
    UpdateRecord --> Ready[processing_status ready]
    PdfOptimize --> Failure[Processing error]
    ImageOptimize --> Failure
    Failure --> Fallback[Keep original and store error]
    Fallback --> Ready
